summary: The lost land of Trafia is an new land but still very WIP. It will be like the shivering isles but in the realm of mundas.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4]**Please Note this mod is not dead, I just took a break, I will be back working on it again today**[/size]

This land once part of the the empire but being insignificant it was forgotten over time. Please help me make this a good mod by aiding in the mod. please PM if you would like to help. Thank you to NordRaider88 for your help.

You travel by boat to the lost land, being told you are going on a expedition. You will meet new people and visit new places. Despite being forskaen by the empire the dragons still attack this land. more files will be coming soon.

The King. Some say he is possessed by sheogorath himself. the land of the insane some may say, others say the shivering isles themselves has entered the realm. What do you think?

"Wonderful! Time for a celebration... Cheese for everyone! Wait, scratch that. Cheese for no one. That can be just as much of a celebration, if you don't like cheese, true? You've run a maze like a good little rat. But no cheese for you yet. Well, maybe a little."- Sheogorath

Visit the main Thread at Dark Creations. http://www.darkcreations.org/forums/forum/534-trafia/

Things complete so far:
The village of Ramlit
